---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-12">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-burgundy mb-8 border-b-4 border-gold/30 pb-4 inline-block">Privacy Policy</h1>
    
    <div class="prose lg:prose-lg text-gray-700 max-w-none">
      <p class="lead text-xl text-gray-800 font-medium mb-8">
        At Hebron Matriculation Higher Secondary School, we are committed to protecting your privacy and ensuring the security of your personal information.
      </p>

      <div class="bg-cream/30 p-8 rounded-xl border border-gold/20 mb-8">
        <h3 class="text-burgundy mt-0">Google Analytics</h3>
        <p>
          We use Google Analytics to help us understand how visitors interact with our website. This service collects anonymous usage data, such as:
        </p>
        <ul class="marker:text-burgundy">
          <li>Pages you visit and time spent on them.</li>
          <li>Your approximate location (e.g., country/city).</li>
          <li>Device type and browser information.</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="text-sm italic">
          This data does <strong>not</strong> include personally identifiable information (PII) like your name, email, or phone number. We use these insights solely to improve our website's content and user experience.
        </p>
      </div>

      <h3 class="text-burgundy">Information We Collect</h3>
      <p>
        We do not collect personal information unless you voluntarily provide it, such as when you:
      </p>
      <ul class="marker:text-burgundy">
        <li>Fill out an admission inquiry form.</li>
        <li>Register as an alumni.</li>
        <li>Contact us via email.</li>
      </ul>

      <h3 class="text-burgundy">Cookies</h3>
      <p>
        Our website uses standard cookies to enhance your browsing experience. Cookies are small text files stored on your device that help us remember your preferences. You can control or disable cookies through your browser settings at any time.
      </p>

      <h3 class="text-burgundy">External Links</h3>
      <p>
        Our site may contain links to external websites (e.g., educational resources, government portals). We are not responsible for the content or privacy practices of these third-party sites. We encourage you to review their policies if you leave our domain.
      </p>

      <div class="mt-12 pt-8 border-t border-gray-200">
        <h3 class="text-burgundy mt-0">Contact Us</h3>
        <p>
          If you have questions regarding this Privacy Policy, please contact our administration office:
        </p>
        <p class="font-bold text-gray-900">
          Hebron Matriculation Higher Secondary School<br/>
          <span class="font-normal text-gray-600">Email:</span> hebronngl@yahoo.com
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
